Yes, it would make rains the most powerfull AE spells. Back in beta all AEs hit unlimited targets including rains. So if you have 20 mobs in the radius it would hit all 20 with 3 waves. Rains were the best spells in the game. I suspect that that is why they only score 4 &quot;hits&quot; as opposed to hitting 4 targets 3 times. They were specificly nerfing rains becuase they felt they were way overpowered.<br>
