I can't call the Al'Kabor spells a 'bug' either. It's a &quot;broken&quot; spell line though just like the &lt;50 rains. The 4 hits max nerf when the game went live crippled the Al'Kabor spells completely. Yes, they were limited to 4 targets when the game went live, they were upped to 5 later on after it was pointed out that even hitting 4 targets for full damage wouldn't be as efficient as nuking them with your DD spell of the same level. (and it took several months of repeatedly pointing it out)<br>
